<div class ="container py-5">
<!-- Code for the user title -->
  <div class="row justify-content-center py-5 bg-white text-dark">
    <h1> You chose one of <%= @user.first_name.capitalize  %>'s itineraries </h1>
  </div>
<!-- Code for the user profile pic and profile -->
  <div class="row bg-white text-dark pb-5">
    <div class="col-sm-1"></div>

    <div class="col-sm-5">
          <div class="text-center p-3 mb-3" style="position: relative">
            <div class="card-category-trip" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.3), rgba(0,0,0,0.3)), url(https://res.cloudinary.com/pierreja/image/upload/v1575559925/TRASEU/Sophie%20user%20-%20pages/Bagpackers.jpg)"></div>
            <div class="photo-info">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-sm-5">
      <div class="text-center p-3">
        <h4 class="text-center"><%= @user.first_name.capitalize  %>'s activity on Traseu</h4> <hr>
      </div>

      <div class="text-justify p-3">
        <i class="far fa-flag"> </i> <b> <%= @user.countryoforigin %> </b><br>
        <i class="far fa-envelope"> </i><b> <%= @user.email %> </b><br>
        <i class="fas fa-user-friends"></i><b> Followers: </b><%= @user.follower  %> <br>
        <i class="fas fa-users"></i> <b> Following: </b><%= @user.following  %> <br>
        <i class="fas fa-star"></i> <b> Rating: </b><%= @user.rating  %>  <br>
        <i class="fas fa-map-signs"></i><b> My itineraries: </b> <a href="/itineraries/new?utf8=✓&search%5Bcountry%5D=peru&search%5Bcountry%5D=peru&search%5Bcountry%5D=peru&search%5Bcountry%5D=peru&search%5Bbudget%5D=1500&search%5Bdays%5D=15&button=&search%5Bexperience%5D=urban&search%5Bexperience%5D=adventure&search%5Bexperience%5D=culture&search%5Bexperience%5D=party">Party experience in Peru</a> <%#= link_to @user.itineraryofuser, itinerary_path %> <br>
        <i class="fas fa-globe"></i> <b> Visited countries: </b> <%= @user.country %> <br>

      </div>


      <div class="col-sm-1"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <!-- Code for the user presentation -->

  <div class="row bg-white text-dark pb-5">
    <div class="col-sm-1"></div>
    <div class="col-sm-10 px-3">
      <div class="text-center p-3">
        <h4 class="text-center">Know more about <%= @user.first_name.capitalize  %>:</h4> <hr>
      </div>

      <div class="text-justify p-3">
       <p><%= @user.presentation  %></p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm-1"></div>
<!-- Code for the user carousel of photos -->
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-sm-1"></div>
    <div class="col-sm-10"><div class="text-center p-3">
        <h4 class="text-center"><%= @user.first_name.capitalize  %>'s pictures:</h4> <hr>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm-1"></div>

    <div class="col-sm-1"></div>
    <div class="col-sm-10">
      <div id="carouselExampleControls" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
        <div class="carousel-inner">
          <div class="carousel-item active">
            <img class="d-block w-100" src="https://res.cloudinary.com/pierreja/image/upload/v1575560021/TRASEU/Sophie%20user%20-%20pages/Machu-pichu.jpg" alt="First slide">
          </div>
          <div class="carousel-item">
            <img class="d-block w-100" src="https://res.cloudinary.com/pierreja/image/upload/v1575559986/TRASEU/Sophie%20user%20-%20pages/child.jpg" alt="Second slide">
          </div>
          <div class="carousel-item">
            <img class="d-block w-100" src="https://res.cloudinary.com/pierreja/image/upload/v1575559940/TRASEU/Sophie%20user%20-%20pages/Lama.jpg" alt="Third slide">
          </div>
        </div>
        <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselExampleControls" role="button" data-slide="prev">
          <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
        </a>
        <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselExampleControls" role="button" data-slide="next">
          <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm-1"></div>
  </div>
</div>
<!-- Code for the user reviews -->
  <div class="row bg-white text-dark pb-5">
    <div class="col-sm-1"></div>
    <div class="col-sm-10">
      <div class="text-center p-3">
        <h4 class="text-center"><%= @user.first_name.capitalize  %>' reviews:</h4> <hr>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm-1"></div>
    </div>
<!-- Code for the review 1 -->

  <div class="row bg-white text-dark pb-5">
    <div class="col-sm-1"></div>
    <div class="col-sm-3 text-center">
      <p><b>Marina</b></p>
      <img class="img-circle" src="https://res.cloudinary.com/pierreja/image/upload/v1575560145/TRASEU/Sophie%20user%20-%20pages/Marina.jpg" alt="Marina">
    </div>

    <div class="col-sm-7 text-left">
      <b><i>Fantastic input! <i class="fas fa-star"></i><i class="fas fa-star"></i><i class="fas fa-star"></i><i class="fas fa-star"></i></i></b><br><br>
      <p><i>I tried <%= @user.first_name.capitalize  %>’s itinerary for “Party to Peru” If it wasn’t for <%= @user.first_name.capitalize  %>’s itinerary, I would have missed out quite a lot. Not too fancy but still comfortable, his itineraries are not only relevant but also precious when you are a lonely backpacker like me!</i></p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm-1"></div>
  </div>

<!-- Code for the review 2 -->

  <div class="row bg-white text-dark pb-5">
    <div class="col-sm-1"></div>
    <div class="col-sm-3 text-center">
      <p><b>Javier</b></p>
      <img class="img-circle" src="https://res.cloudinary.com/pierreja/image/upload/v1575560165/TRASEU/Sophie%20user%20-%20pages/javier.jpg" alt="Javier">
    </div>

    <div class="col-sm-7 text-left">
      <b><i>I Wish I read this before! <i class="fas fa-star"><i class="fas fa-star"></i><i class="fas fa-star"></i><i class="fas fa-star"></i><i class="fas fa-star"></i></i></b><br><br>
      <p><i>I have been following <%= @user.first_name.capitalize  %> for 6 month, and I agree with each and every single word <%= @user.first_name.capitalize  %> writes. It’s simple but efficient advice as well as original and genuine itineraries that allowed me to meet locals, not only tourists.</i></p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm-1"></div>
  </div>

<!-- Code for the review 3 -->

  <div class="row bg-white text-dark pb-5">
    <div class="col-sm-1"></div>
    <div class="col-sm-3 text-center">
      <p><b>Bob</b></p>
      <img class="img-circle" src="https://res.cloudinary.com/pierreja/image/upload/v1575560183/TRASEU/Sophie%20user%20-%20pages/bob.jpg" alt="Bob">
    </div>

    <div class="col-sm-7 text-left">
      <b><i>Great advice! <i class="fas fa-star"><i class="fas fa-star"></i><i class="fas fa-star"></i><i class="fas fa-star"></i><i class="fas fa-star"></i></i></b><br><br>
      <p><i>At first I was skeptical when I read <%= @user.first_name.capitalize  %>’s itinerary, but after reading the reviews, I figured “why not?”. I gave a try to the “Party to Peru” itinerary, and it is probably the best way to visit a country I received. If anyone knows Peru, it’s definitely <%= @user.first_name.capitalize  %>!</i></p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm-1"></div>
  </div>


</div>
</div>
